    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"310045\">Eric Wieser</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/270676-lean4/topic/max.20recursion.20depth.20reached.20on.20.60simp.20.5BgetElem.5D.60/near/449734721\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Try doing <code>simp only [getElem]</code> followed by <code>simp?</code> to find it</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Ah. The simp theorem <code>Array.get_eq_getElem</code> is doing it.</p>",
