    {
        "content": "<p>The reason that I was adding <code>getElem</code> was that <code>simp</code> does not close the goal (which seems a bit surprising to me).</p>",
        "id": 449746943,
        "sender_full_name": "David Renshaw",
        "timestamp": 1720402046
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This works:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">only</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">getElem</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Array</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">get</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">get</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
